headline: AI Push Powers Amphenol Corporation (NYSE:APH) Higher—But TD Cowen Says Hold Despite Target Hike
summary: TD Cowen earlier this month raised the price target on Amphenol Corporation (NYSE:APH) to $70 from $63 and kept a Hold rating on the shares. Amphenol specializes in designing, manufacturing, and marketing electrical, electronic, and fiber optic connectors. The advisory said the AI ramp had been incredible, and numbers kept moving higher.
